"title": "5876: helpfulness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5876",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>God's help</h2>\n<h3>God promises his help</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:3-Ps121:4\">PSA 121:3–121:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a></p>\n<h3>People value God's help</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:6-Ps118:7\">PSA 118:6–118:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:29\">DEU 33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:8\">2CH 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:4\">PSA 54:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:9\">ISA 50:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22\">ACT 26:22</a></p>\n<h3>People need God's help</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:17\">PSA 94:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:12\">JOS 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:11\">PSA 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:19\">PSA 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:17\">PSA 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:6\">PSA 116:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:16\">ISA 59:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:5\">ISA 63:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:6-Ps118:7\">PSA 118:6–118:7</a></p>\n<h3>God's help can be withheld</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:42\">2SA 22:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:7\">JOB 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:11-Ps107:13\">PSA 107:11–107:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:9\">HOS 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:13\">ZEC 7:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's help is not imposed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:12\">JER 29:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:11-2Kgs5:12\">2KI 5:11–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:12\">2CH 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6-1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:6–5:7</a></p>\n<h3>People should imitate God's help by being helpful</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:1\">2SA 9:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:36-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:36–10:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:2\">GAL 6:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">EPH 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:17\">JAS 2:14–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of human helpfulness</h2>\n<h3>Shown to those in need</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:34\">LUK 10:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:15\">2CH 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:15-Job29:16\">JOB 29:15–29:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:44–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:34-Acts4:35\">ACT 4:34–4:35</a></p>\n<h3>Shown by young people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1SA 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:15\">1SA 17:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17\">1SA 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:36\">1SA 20:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:2-2Kgs5:3\">2KI 5:2–5:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:9\">JHN 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>Shown within marriage</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:18\">GEN 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:22\">GEN 2:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:22\">PRO 18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:12\">PRO 31:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:20\">PRO 31:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Shown to God's servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:2\">ROM 16:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:4\">JOS 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:15\">JOS 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:10-1Kgs17:11\">1KI 17:10–17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:7\">LUK 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15-1Cor16:16\">1CO 16:15–16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:11\">2CO 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:3\">PHP 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:11\">PHM 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Helpfulness is remembered and rewarded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:34–25:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:17\">JOS 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:14\">1KI 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:2\">ROM 16:2</a></p>",
